  "original_title": "Public requested to send photo or video evidence on fuel hoarders",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Public requested to send photo or video evidence on fuel hoarders",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Power & Energy has appealed to the general public to send video or photo evidence of people hoarding or illegally selling fuel or not following instructions on fuel distribution.",
        "The ministry said it will suspend the QR pass issued to such persons or seek legal actions against them.",
        "Photo or video evidence of such people can be sent to 074 212 3123."
      ],
